casebody.data:
No. 10-11055 (10A1235). Eddie D. Powell, Petitioner v. Kim Thomas, Interim Commissioner, Alabama Department of Corrections, et al. 564 U.S. 1015, 131 S. Ct. 3018,

180 L. Ed. 2d 842,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 4561. June 16, 2011.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death, presented to Justice Thomas, and by him referred to the Court, denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied.

Same case below, 643 F.3d 1300.
